text: Johan Flodin (born 29 July 1967) is a Swedish rower. He competed in the men's quadruple sculls event at the 1996 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1967 births Category:Living people Category:Swedish male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Sweden Category:Rowers at the 1996 Summer Olympics Category:People from Mölndal
